snippet.title: Astral Gun Trailer
snippet.description:
Astral gun is the hyper-competitive 2-4 player party game focused on exciting, intense, and hardcore matches. Create your own playstyle with 14 unique weapons.

Available on Steam Now!

Learn more at www.AstralGun.com
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/416850
Follow development at twitter.com/ThomasMoonKang
Developed by Thomas Moon Kang
